.SH NAME
__bio_iov_iter_get_pages \- pin user or kernel pages and add them to a bio
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" __bio_iov_iter_get_pages
.BI "(struct bio *bio "  ","
.BI "struct iov_iter *iter "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bio" 12
bio to add pages to
.IP "iter" 12
iov iterator describing the region to be mapped
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Pins pages from *iter and appends them to \fIbio\fP's bvec array. The
pages will have to be released using \fBput_page\fP when done.
For multi-segment *iter, this function only adds pages from the
next non-empty segment of the iov iterator.
